{
  "id": "6a03d54511f7c56a8c541db6",
  "title": "ルールを決める話は面白そうとは思う",
  "created": 1778636102,
  "updated": 1778636107,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a03d54511f7c56a8c541db6",
      "text": "ルールを決める話は面白そうとは思う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615a6",
      "text": "from [2025/06/07]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636107
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615a8",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615a9",
      "text": "\tルールを決める話は面白そうとは思う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615aa",
      "text": "\t 懸念",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615ab",
      "text": "\t  [ルール守ってるからいいだろ]みたいな雰囲気になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615ac",
      "text": "\t   ルールの隅を突くのが好きな人が多いイメージ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615ad",
      "text": "\t    結果良いルールになるかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615ae",
      "text": "\t  [ルールが形骸化]する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615af",
      "text": "\t   ルール直すのが好きそうな人が多いので、大丈夫か？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b0",
      "text": "\t  ルールだらけになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b1",
      "text": "\t   めちゃありそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b2",
      "text": "\t  合意を取る仕組みがない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b3",
      "text": "\t 懸念はあるが試みは面白そう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b4",
      "text": "\t 良い懸念なので、これもRFCにできそうですね[yuki_minoh.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b5",
      "text": "\t 　井戸端RFCを盲信するなよ、的なRFCもあって良いなと思ってます",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b6",
      "text": "\t 　RFCが増える一方なのはありそう。。。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b7",
      "text": "\t 　infoboxなら対抗できたりしないかな。。。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b8",
      "text": "\t 　一旦、RFC新規作成を歓迎する方針で[井戸端RFC 003: 井戸端RFCの運用]としました",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03d54600000000007615b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778636102,
      "updated": 1778636102
    }
  ]
}